textAfterTable: Refunds Refunds are available for annual and term permits.  Short-term permits such as daily, monthly, or weekly permits are not eligible for refunds.   Faculty/Staff who no longer need a parking permit may be eligible for a pro-rated refund until the last business day of March. In order to be eligible for a refund, individuals must complete a cancellation card and submit it to the Auxiliary Service Business Office located in the University Union.  The refund amount will be determined by the date the cancellation is received.  Please contact the Auxiliary Services Business Office, 410-704-2284, for more details.
